295
00:26:44,336 --> 00:26:49,877
to give emphasis to a major event, which is a turning point in the pacing.

296
00:26:53,818 --> 00:26:57,819
So I played with the rhythm of the action.

297
00:26:59,199 --> 00:27:03,240
We go from a slow rhythm before the creature arrives.

298
00:27:04,051 --> 00:27:07,354
to a fast and very stressful situation,

299
00:27:11,617 --> 00:27:15,480
with a moment of suspension, when you have to backtrack.

300
00:27:28,170 --> 00:27:31,813
Then, to reach the climax, where another punctuation...

301
00:27:32,785 --> 00:27:34,406
surprise again the player.

