00:30:36,875 --> 00:30:38,936
about the core gameplay.

328
00:30:39,776 --> 00:30:43,318
Something around fighting, but also a means for protection.

329
00:30:44,618 --> 00:30:48,020
After the escape from jail, the initial idea

330
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:52,842
was to progress from one shelter to another

