00:34:03,753 --> 00:34:04,594
by Japanese

367
00:34:05,214 --> 00:34:12,459
manga animation, in which we get an impression of high-speed movement just by stretching lines.

368
00:34:25,980 --> 00:34:31,521
This is the end of the jail level, where Buddy and Lester are separated.

